{"data":[{"date":"07:06 03/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Palestine b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/olympic-viet-nam-se-doi-dau-palestine-bang-doi-hinh-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khai m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 3/8. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>1. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 mang theo hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. V\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y Park l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: &ldquo;Theo t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1, V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u1edf FLC Thanh Ho\u00e1.&nbsp;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Palestine nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Palestine nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Doi-hinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-se-doi-dau-Palestine-nhu-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, qua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i V\u0103n Thanh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 H\u1ed3ng Duy l\u1eabn Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n Thanh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00ea H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u0103n Thanh ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Trung v\u1ec7 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y, sau khi Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh, t\u1ef1 tin, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ed7 d\u1ef1a tinh th\u1ea7n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung ve Bui Tien Dung ghi ban cho Viettel trong ngay thay Park den du khan\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ghi b\u00e0n cho Viettel trong ng\u00e0y th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/28/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-du-khan,-trung-ve-Bui-Tien-Dung-toa-sang-ruc-ro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Trung v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Palestine. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Duy M\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 cao t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, l\u0103n x\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>5. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 cao trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1n xuy\u1ebfn kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tho\u00e1t thua \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng, v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\">HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>6. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i SLNA, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u1edf V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phan Van Duc dang co phong do cao voi bon ban sau ba tran gan nhat.\" title=\"Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao v\u1edbi b\u1ed1n b\u00e0n sau ba tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/a1-7074-1530882860.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>7. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Palestine s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao HAGL th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng \u00edt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Do \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>8. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u01a1i trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, l\u0103n x\u1ea3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i gi\u00e0u t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 1 trong s\u1ed1 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 20 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993. V\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Palestine c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien ve Do Hung Dung\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-viet-nam-co-hoi-nao-cho-nhom-tan-binh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-co-hoi-nao-cho-nhom-tan-binh-168-192576.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-viet-nam-co-hoi-nao-cho-nhom-tan-binh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-co-hoi-nao-cho-nhom-tan-binh-168-192576.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh?</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n9. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Quang H\u1ea3i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng Quang H\u1ea3i. L\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, Quang H\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 nh\u01b0ng khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a khi nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Tuy nhi\u00ean Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng &lsquo;n\u00f3ng m\u00e1y&rsquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t V-League 2018 l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00fang hai b\u00e0n. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Vinaphone Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>10. H\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ed9ng, thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Do \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Park Hang Seo trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong chua co the luc tot nhat sau khi vua binh phuc chan thuong\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau khi v\u1eeba b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/cong-phuong-truot-bai-kiem-tra-the-luc-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>11. Trung phong Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33 song Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung phong c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Vi\u1ec7c anh xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho th\u1ea5y ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1edbi Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi V-League 2017.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u00fap anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t &lsquo;s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m&rsquo; \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. Do \u0111\u00f3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park trong th\u1eddi gian ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, Ti\u1ebfn Linh tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-038-cho-con-mua-ban-thang-168-192600.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-038-cho-con-mua-ban-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-038-cho-con-mua-ban-thang-168-192600.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine (19h30 ng\u00e0y 3/8): Ch\u1edd c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 hai \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine \u0111\u1ec1u tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/lineup.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1936","checkdouble":"192601"},{"date":"07:24 03/08","title":"Barca s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gia World Cup trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea nh\u1eafm Zaha n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri, Chelsea m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t Jorginho l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robert Green ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Cuc-nong-Wilfried-Zaha-muon-toi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilfried Zaha c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea n\u1ebfu Willian ho\u1eb7c Hazard ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ebft c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Theo Mirror, Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua d\u00f9 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U ghi t\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh gi\u00fap Palace tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Willian v\u00e0 Eden Hazard \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Zaha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Zaha b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea, theo Mirror, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Stamford&nbsp;Bridge.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/Muc-tieu-50-trieu-bang-bat-den-xanh-cho-Chelsea-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zaha mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda Palace \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Zaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n, anh c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/co-doi-bong-chi-40-trieu-bang-mua-hang-thai-mu-172-182476.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Zaha</span>, song ph\u00eda Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Palace y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Spurs ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea, n\u1ebfu The Blues th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1935","checkdouble":"192602"},{"date":"07:45 03/08","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/10/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-dong-y-o-lai-serie-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Alessandro Florenzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AS Roma k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi CLB Chelsea.</h2><h2>Florenzi gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Roma</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin CLB Chelsea mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Alessandro Florenzi c\u1ee7a AS Roma. Theo t\u1edd&nbsp;Corriere dello Sport, Alessandro Florenzi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n&nbsp;t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng&nbsp;s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U va Barca muon co Alessandro Florenzi\" title=\"M.U v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alessandro Florenzi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/10/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-dong-y-o-lai-serie-a.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Florenzi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AS Roma</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Florenzi \u0111ang b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i Roma, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. Tuy nhi\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Serie A.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 Roma \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Olimpico b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2023. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi Florenzi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Chelsea m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Inter Milan v\u00e0 Atletico Madrid \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Roma.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Florenzi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 224 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 cho AS Roma v\u00e0 28 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Italia. Anh ch\u01a1i thu\u1ea7n \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu-172-192598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu-172-192598.html\">N\u00f3ng: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay M.U</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i Joel Pereira \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay M.U \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Vitoria Setubal theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi-187-192602.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi-187-192602.html\">Barca s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gia World Cup trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Diario Sport, CLB Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal, Moussa Wagu\u00e9, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1934","checkdouble":"192603"},{"date":"08:05 03/08","title":"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/12/18/4-doi-bong-hoi-mua-marcos-rojo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Everton mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Marcos Rojo r\u1eddi MU, theo The Sun, ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng th\u00ec 3 CLB kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/everton-chi-chap-nhan-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-neu-172-192428.html\" target=\"_blank\">Everton mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rojo</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/4-doi-bong-muon-dua-hau-ve-Marcos-Rojo-roi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Marcos Rojo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd h\u01a1pk \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu anh gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb 120.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n xu\u1ed1ng 60.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990. Theo The Sun, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 3 CLB <br>\r\nkh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, PSG, Marseille v\u00e0 Zenit St Petersburg c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Marcos Rojo v\u1edbi Everton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Marcos Rojo ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u CLB mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Marcos Rojo r\u1eddi MU, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/16/4-doi-bong-dai-chien-vi-sao-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, M.U \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t Mina c\u1ee7a Barca l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Barca h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Marcos Rojo thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, vi\u1ec7c anh ra \u0111i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 t\u00e2n binh kh\u1ee7ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Fred v\u00e0 Dalot l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1933","checkdouble":"192604"},{"date":"08:19 03/08","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \"b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh\" cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/zaha-moi-goi-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea nh\u1eafm Zaha n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri, Chelsea m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t Jorginho l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robert Green ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Cuc-nong-Wilfried-Zaha-muon-toi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilfried Zaha c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea n\u1ebfu Willian ho\u1eb7c Hazard ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ebft c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Theo Mirror, Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua d\u00f9 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U ghi t\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh gi\u00fap Palace tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Willian v\u00e0 Eden Hazard \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Zaha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Zaha b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea, theo Mirror, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Stamford&nbsp;Bridge.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/Muc-tieu-50-trieu-bang-bat-den-xanh-cho-Chelsea-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zaha mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda Palace \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Zaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n, anh c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/co-doi-bong-chi-40-trieu-bang-mua-hang-thai-mu-172-182476.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Zaha</span>, song ph\u00eda Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Palace y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Spurs ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea, n\u1ebfu The Blues th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1932","checkdouble":"192605"},{"date":"08:22 03/08","title":"V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, M.U v\u00e0 Inter c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real ra gi\u00e1 Modric cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia, nh\u1eefng Man United hay Inter Milan s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 750 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Modric \u0111\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32, Luka Modric v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3ng vai \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u gi\u00fap Croatia gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. T\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra, Modric \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real ra gi\u00e1 Modric cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real ra gi\u00e1 Modric cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Real-ra-gia-Modric-cho-cac-doi-tac-theo-duoi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Modric t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau gi\u1ea3i, Modric tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;h\u00e0ng hot&rdquo; tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Man United v\u00e0 Inter Milan \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nReal b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i hy v\u1ecdng Modric s\u1ebd g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf l\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Mesut Ozil\" title=\"tien ve Mesut Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/tien-ve-Modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real ra gi\u00e1 Modric l\u00ean t\u1edbi 750 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng d\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o tham v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu anh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Real ra gi\u00e1 Modric. &ldquo;Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Modric l\u00e0 b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 750 tri\u1ec7u Euro&rdquo;, Perez n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Modric v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau World Cup 2018. Anh c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2020 v\u1edbi Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nong-hlv-real-bat-ngo-che-thibaut-courtois-180-192594.html\">N\u00f3ng: HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd &ldquo;ch\u00ea&rdquo; Thibaut Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-madrid-tin-tuong-gareth-bale-thay-the-ronaldo-180-192589.html\">Kh\u00f4ng mua ai thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo, t\u00e2n HLV Real Madrid tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Gareth Bale</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/mourinho-muon-mu-chieu-mo-bo-doi-cua-real-187-192515.html\">Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho-184-192497.html\">Sao Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-viec-real-mua-courtois-180-192483.html\">HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1931","checkdouble":"192606"},{"date":"08:42 03/08","title":"Neuer: \u201cOzil c\u1ee9 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/neuer-phat-bieu-ve-ozil-va-quyet-dinh-giai-nghe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Neuer ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich l\u1ea1i \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 tr\u00ean \u0110TQG.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ozil chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean v\u1edbi Mesut Ozil. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i, anh b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i b\u1edfi cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, Recep Tayyip Erdogan. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Erdogan l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh kh\u00e1ch b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac, gi\u00f4ng b\u00e3o v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha Ozil. \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng ph\u00ea b\u00ecnh t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neuer ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Neuer ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/neuer-phat-bieu-ve-ozil-va-quyet-dinh-giai-nghe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ozil chia tay \u0110T\u00a0\u0110\u1ee9c sau World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ee9c n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ee1 b\u1edd, Ozil tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e3i v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 th\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c (DFB).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Neuer \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern Munich, Uli Hoeness ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Neuer ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Neuer mac sai lam\" title=\"thu mon Neuer mac sai lam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/thu-thanh-neuer-noi-gi-ve-tran-thua-soc-cua-dt-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neuer ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Bayern th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Ozil v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111i qu\u00e1 xa. \u201cN\u1ebfu Ozil v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y\u201d, Neuer n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng b\u1edfi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Ozil kh\u00f4ng, Neuer tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi: \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u201d, anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cKhi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang anh \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 l\u00fd do c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5. \u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia sau m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Euro hay World Cup.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/quoc-te/cdv-duc-bieu-tinh-bang-co-tho-nhi-ky-de-ung-ho-ozil-290-192417.html\">C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c bi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1edd Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ozil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly-p2-389-192316.html\">T\u00e2m th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil: Gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00e0n ly (P2)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hai-trai-tim-cua-mesut-ozil-va-duc-hanh-an-khuat-trong-nen-bong-da-hien-dai-184-192160.html\">\u201cHai tr\u00e1i tim\u201d c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9c h\u1ea1nh \u1ea9n khu\u1ea5t trong n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-bi-duc-ruong-bo-da-co-tho-nhi-ky-lo-172-191936.html\">Ozil b\u1ecb \u0110\u1ee9c ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf? \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 lo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ozil-tiep-tuc-bi-danh-hoi-dong-tu-tuyen-duc-421-191879.html\">Ozil ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1eeb tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1930","checkdouble":"192607"},{"date":"08:06 03/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 3/8: M.U \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi sao Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-38-mu-dat-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-sao-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi sao Barca, S\u1ebfp Bayern Munich ch\u00ea Juve v\u00ec mua Ronaldo, Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 3/8.</h2><h2>M.U&nbsp;\u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n&nbsp;v\u1edbi Yerry Mina</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o Mundo Deprotivo (T\u00e2y Ban Nha) \u0111\u01b0a tin&nbsp;Yerry Mina&nbsp;v\u00e0 M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.&nbsp;Theo \u0111\u00f3 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Barca l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, Barca ra gi\u00e1 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Mina tuy nhi\u00ean M.U ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia t\u1eeb Palmeiras h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1/2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 38 MU \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Yerry Mina  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 38 MU \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Yerry Mina  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-28-Juventus-va-Milan-hoan-tat-thuong-vu-hoan-doi-ngoi-sao-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Yerry Mina</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Gonzalo Higuain<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng CLB AC Milan c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c cho ra m\u1eb7t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Real, Gonzalo Higuain. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus v\u1edbi th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o h\u00e8 2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&nbsp;Gonzalo Higuain, Milan ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3&nbsp;Leonardo Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus \u0111\u00fang 1 n\u0103m mua trung v\u1ec7 Italia n\u00e0y t\u1eeb L\u00e3o b\u00e0. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Juventus ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng 24 tu\u1ed5i&nbsp;Mattia Caldara gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Bayern ra m\u1eaft tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 &lsquo;0 \u0111\u1ed3ng&rsquo;<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba qua, Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Leon Goretzka theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do sau khi anh \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Schalke 04 (v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 30/6 v\u1eeba qua).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 t\u1edbi t\u1eadn h\u00f4m nay, H\u00f9m x\u00e1m m\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng t\u00e2n binh gi\u00e1 &lsquo;0 \u0111\u1ed3ng&rsquo; n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Goretzka, Bayern \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i gia ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Barcelona hay Juventus. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00f9m x\u00e1m s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi ra kho\u1ea3ng 20 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ti\u00eau sau 2 n\u0103m \u1edf MU<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool t\u1ea1i ICC 2018, HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o MU v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Nh\u00e0 H\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1&nbsp;nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng&nbsp;m\u00e0 \u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016 t\u1edbi nay, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t&nbsp;Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a MU s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 382 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau&nbsp;mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, \u00f4ng c\u00f2n mang v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Paul Pogba t\u1eeb Juve v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>S\u1ebfp Bayern Munich ch\u00ea Juve thi\u1ebfu l\u00ed tr\u00ed khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, G\u0110\u0110H c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich l\u00e0 Karl-Heinz Rummenigge cho r\u1eb1ng H\u00f9m x\u00e1m s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ra c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo nh\u01b0 CLB Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Cristiano Ronaldo sao? T\u00f4i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Andrea Agnelli quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh theo \u0111u\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 chi ti\u00eau m\u1ea1nh tay nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u00ean g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 Juventus, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y h\u1ee3p l\u00fd b\u1edfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Juve \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4n ngoan. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 t\u1ea5t tay v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Vidal l\u1ecdt &lsquo;t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm&rsquo; Barcelona<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arturo Vidal \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm CLB Barcelona trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 20 tri\u1ec7u euro (17,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Vidal \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn Inter Milan. Ngo\u00e0i Vidal, m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal Moussa Wague, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u Phi ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Darmian s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi gian qua, M.U \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eafng nghe l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Juventus v\u00e0 Napoli cho Matteo Darmian. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh. H\u1ecd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Darmian thay v\u00ec b\u00e1n \u0111i b\u1edfi \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Tullio Tinti c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Italy chia s\u1ebb. &ldquo;Napoli \u01b0? Mourinho v\u00e0 M.U kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Darmian r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Sau cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129, Darmian s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chia tay M.U trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9&nbsp;n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, \u00f4ng Graeme Jones kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc Thibaut s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 n\u0103m trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ra \u0111i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh G\u0103ng tay V\u00e0ng \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1edbi&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXEM TH\u00caM:&nbsp;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-28-juventus-va-milan-hoan-tat-thuong-vu-hoan-doi-ngoi-sao-184-192578.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 2/8: Juventus v\u00e0 Milan ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi-187-192602.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi-187-192602.html\">Barca s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gia World Cup trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Diario Sport, CLB Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal, Moussa Wagu\u00e9, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu-172-192598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu-172-192598.html\">N\u00f3ng: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay M.U</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i Joel Pereira \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay M.U \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Vitoria Setubal theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1929","checkdouble":"192608"},{"date":"08:51 03/08","title":"MU v\u00e0 Tottenham nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb \"m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t\" c\u1ee7a Watford","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/9/mu-va-tottenham-nhan-tin-buon-tu-doucoure.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Abdoulaye Doucoure gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Watford, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 Tottenham trong vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Abdoulaye Doucoure</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Abdoulaye Doucoure l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Watford. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, anh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Abdoulaye Doucoure gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Watford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Abdoulaye Doucoure gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Watford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/Abdoulaye-Doucoure-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Watford-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Abdoulaye Doucoure \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng Doucoure tranh ch\u1ea5p c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, anh c\u0169ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o khi ghi t\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a 2017/18, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/watford-chot-gia-ban-may-quet-cho-liverpool-172-183144.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Doucoure</span>, M.U v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Watford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Everton l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993. HLV Marco Silva mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Goodison Park, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Everton v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Doucoure.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u1ebft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Doucoure</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Abdoulaye Doucoure gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Watford, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Javi Gracia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Vicarage Road.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Abdoulaye Doucoure\" title=\"Abdoulaye Doucoure\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/20/DHTB-vong-12-Premier-League-Vinh-danh-Salah-va-Hazard-hinh-anh-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Abdoulaye Doucoure \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Watford th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Doucoure l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, t\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng Doucoure \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Watford. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui khi gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDoucoure gia nh\u1eadp Watford v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2016 t\u1eeb Rennes Lennes, hi\u1ec7n anh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1928","checkdouble":"192609"},{"date":"06:46 03/08","title":"Tottenham c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1n binh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u00ean TTCN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Mauricio Pochettino th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn nguy c\u01a1 Spurs c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda \u1edf Anh trong v\u00f2ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng, nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ed1i \u0111u\u00f4i nhau, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t l\u1eafm ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a nh\u01b0 Premier League. V\u00e0 th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 Tottenham, \u00e1 qu\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh 2/3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n im h\u01a1i l\u1eb7ng ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00e8 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00e8 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/Chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-he-2018-co-the-khong-chieu-mo-tan-binh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mauricio Pochettino th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, vi\u1ec7c Spurs \u00e1n binh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi lo l\u1eafng, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1ea5p r\u00fat t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n hay ch\u00ed \u00edt t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay c\u1ea3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n HLV Mauricio Pochettino c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn nguy c\u01a1 Tottenham c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda \u1edf Anh trong v\u00f2ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina: \u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 cho c\u00e1c anh m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0ng n\u0103m nay th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft CLB c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o n\u1eefa kh\u00f4ng trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 1-2-3-4 nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 ai h\u1ebft.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00fat ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u1edf Anh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn so v\u1edbi Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i, \u0111a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u00e0 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng theo n\u00f3 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-tottenham-he-2018-kho-quen-roi-suong-khong-chiu-duoc-172-192495.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/chuyen-nhuong-tottenham-he-2018-kho-quen-roi-suong-khong-chiu-duoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-tottenham-he-2018-kho-quen-roi-suong-khong-chiu-duoc-172-192495.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00e8 2018: Kh\u1ed5 quen r\u1ed3i, s\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c!</span><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian\u2026\u201d \u2013 Mauricio Pochettino chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft FA Cup c\u1ee7a Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Manchester United, \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1927","checkdouble":"192588"},{"date":"06:26 03/08","title":"Kh\u00f4ng mua ai thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo, t\u00e2n HLV Real Madrid tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi X\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c k\u1ebf th\u1eeba v\u00e0 c\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0n anh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i sau khi ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Zinedine Zidane c\u0169ng v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a Gareth Bale gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn n\u00e0o tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Bernabeu.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui tin Bale thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo \u1edf Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui tin Bale thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo \u1edf Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/HLV-Lopetegui-tin-Bale-thay-the-Ronaldo-o-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Lopetegui tin Bale thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u1ea4y v\u1eady m\u00e0 nh\u01b0 l\u00fac ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ngay sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n hai th\u00e1ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi X\u1ee9 Wales v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Anh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man Utd ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Tottenham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Gareth Bale \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c k\u1ebf th\u1eeba v\u00e0 c\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0n anh Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i sau khi ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cKhi t\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Cristiano v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng s\u1edbm b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ea5t \u0111i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Cristiano ra sao, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Los Blancos. K\u1ebf th\u1eeba di s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y sao cho x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Gareth Bale s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau-180-192564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau-180-192564.html\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid: Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u?</span><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh ch\u00e2n nh\u01b0 v\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1926","checkdouble":"192589"},{"date":"05:39 03/08","title":"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee9a th\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n t\u1ef7 cho t\u1ea5m HCV ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-viet-nam-duoc-hua-thuong-tien-ty-cho-tam-hcv-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c CLB t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean k\u00eanh Youtube.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/CLB-HAGL-bat-ngo-vuon-len-dan-dau-tai-chau-A-ve-suc-hut-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB HAGL d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean Youtube</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Depor&amp;Finanzas v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 trong th\u00e1ng 7 khi thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2,75 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean Youtube. Con s\u1ed1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Buriram (ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n 2,2 tri\u1ec7u).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 HAGL &lsquo;v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 y\u00eau th\u00edch t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Vi\u1ec7c HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y NHM ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ng\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi trong th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1, ho\u00e0 1 v\u00e0 thua \u0111\u1ebfn 2&nbsp;tr\u1eadn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;c\u1ea1nh tranh&rdquo; g\u1eaft gao v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a HAGL nh\u1eefng n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ed1p 10 l\u00e0 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 1,6 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem. X\u1ebfp tr\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Persib Bandung, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Indonesia.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam-168-192384.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam-168-192384.html\">HLV HAGL tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV HAGL \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1925","checkdouble":"192593"},{"date":"05:54 03/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u201cch\u00ea\u201d Thibaut Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/nong-hlv-real-bat-ngo-che-thibaut-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, t\u00e2n HLV Real, Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas, qua \u0111\u00f3 xua tan nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois.</h2><h2>HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd &ldquo;ch\u00ea&rdquo; Thibaut Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u00ea Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng HLV Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u00ea Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Nong-HLV-Real-bat-ngo-che-Thibaut-Courtois-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Real kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua Thibaut Courtois&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Keylor Navas \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Real Madrid trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 31, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 Real \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Thibaut Courtois nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf cho Navas.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u1ee7a Los Blancos l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 d\u1eedng d\u01b0ng v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Real. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Navas v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Navas r\u1ea5t t\u00e2m huy\u1ebft v\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui cho th\u1ea5y Real Madrid \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Thibaut Courtois. H\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 l\u00ean Chelsea b\u1edfi l\u1ebd th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi The Blues. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1t ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi&nbsp;Courtois trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Courtois, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng Thibaut Courtois \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 sang n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:&#10;16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1924","checkdouble":"192594"},{"date":"06:08 03/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (3/8/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-382018.jpg","new_de