esheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai HAGL m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c CLB t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean k\u00eanh Youtube.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB HAGL b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/CLB-HAGL-bat-ngo-vuon-len-dan-dau-tai-chau-A-ve-suc-hut-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB HAGL d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean Youtube</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Depor&amp;Finanzas v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 trong th\u00e1ng 7 khi thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2,75 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem tr\u00ean Youtube. Con s\u1ed1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Buriram (ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n 2,2 tri\u1ec7u).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 HAGL &lsquo;v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 y\u00eau th\u00edch t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Vi\u1ec7c HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y NHM ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ng\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi trong th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1, ho\u00e0 1 v\u00e0 thua \u0111\u1ebfn 2&nbsp;tr\u1eadn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;c\u1ea1nh tranh&rdquo; g\u1eaft gao v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a HAGL nh\u1eefng n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ed1p 10 l\u00e0 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 1,6 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem. X\u1ebfp tr\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Persib Bandung, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Indonesia.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam-168-192384.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam-168-192384.html\">HLV HAGL tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV HAGL \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1922","checkdouble":"192596"}]}